		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah the information is pretty sparse this year, even in Swedish.<br /><br />Like how do the concerts work? Are they just using the same venue? Will be a challenge considering how overcrowded the place was last year. And what about the contests? Judging by the shoddy performance last year, I'd wager I have a pretty good stab at the SMB speedrun competition, but there's no information about which version of the game is being played.<br /><br />You also have to really dig just to find ticket information... seems you just buy entrance at the venue this time, so I'm expecting to end up spending a few hours in that line <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" />

		

