		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When you live outside of Sweden though, that is pretty much invisible.<br />The queue was huge last year, but very very fast (because they had a special entrance for people who bought in advance, which you can't do this year). Not that it mattered to me, as I helped manage a booth there and had a free pass.<br /><br />Unless they are planning to have a shitton of people manning the entrance to let in lots of people simultaneously, I don't see any way they could make it fast. There will always be a lot of people who are super slow when it comes to handling payments.<br />.... So I'm hoping that's what they'll do. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

